PEOPLE(i, e) = people.i.aproximar?e:EST_ID -> people.i.chegar.e -> people.i.esperar.e -> people.i.entrar.e -> people.i.sair.e -> STOP
--TESTE2 = PEOPLE(1) ||| PEOPLE(2) ||| PEOPLE(3) ||| PEOPLE(4) ||| PEOPLE(5)

